{"tid":1833772,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"鼠年竹鼠殺到.... 【武漢肺炎】鍾南山出來，麻煩嚟了","createTime":"2020-01-22T05:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T06:03:13.000Z","uid":281370,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ef28e81252e4f5621f9b18716b790d1f2f74e04a","tid":1833772,"uid":281370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:15:12.000Z","msg":"狗年瘋狗症，豬年非洲豬瘟，鼠年&hellip;竹鼠來了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明年玄空飛星二黑病符星飛和三煞凶星飛至南方，又遇上鍾<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">南</span></strong>山！<br />\n好像冥冥中自有天意......。<br />\n南方包括湖北、南（古楚國），希望天佑香港，唔好吹到來。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】鍾南山推斷病毒源頭疑為竹鼠 近年成餐桌美食<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1685409/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%8D%BE%E5%8D%97%E5%B1%B1%E6%8E%A8%E6%96%B7%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%BA%90%E9%A0%AD%E7%96%91%E7%82%BA%E7%AB%B9%E9%BC%A0-%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B4%E6%88%90%E9%A4%90%E6%A1%8C%E7%BE%8E%E9%A3%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1685409%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%258D%25BE%25E5%258D%2597%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E6%258E%25A8%25E6%2596%25B7%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592%25E6%25BA%2590%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%25AB%25B9%25E9%25BC%25A0-%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%25A4%2590%25E6%25A1%258C%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%25A3%259F&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmCHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=1cb8b404\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1685409%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%258D%25BE%25E5%258D%2597%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E6%258E%25A8%25E6%2596%25B7%25E7%2597%2585%25E